## Caching & Performance

- Redis cache manager: [app/core/cache.py](mdc:app/core/cache.py) → `cache_manager`
- Property cache helpers: `PropertyCacheManager`
- Decorator for ad-hoc caching: `cache_key_wrapper(prefix, ttl=300, key_params=[...])`

### Property List Caching
- Use `PropertyCacheManager.get_cached_properties()` and `.cache_properties()` for unified property search responses.

### Middleware
- Performance timing: [app/middleware/performance.py](mdc:app/middleware/performance.py)
- Enable in [app/main.py](mdc:app/main.py) via `app.add_middleware(PerformanceMiddleware)`

